messages.name: Maggie Tiernan
messages.text:
Hey everyone! Check out this opportunity with OSU AIRC! 


Tech Talk: Leveraging AI/ML Use Cases in the Financial Sector: Challenges and Opportunities
Speaker: Dee Pai, Chief Data Scientist at Chase
📅 Date: Thursday, March 27th, 2025
⏰ Time: 7:30 - 9:00 PM EST
📍 Location: Pomerene Hall 160
🍕 Pizza, cookies, and drinks included!
📝 Resume drop available for attendees!

messages.name: Maggie Tiernan
messages.text: Hey BDAA! Join us this Tuesday, April 1st at 7:30 PM in Pomerene 260 for an in-depth session on NLP and text analysis - exploring how technology is transforming the way we understand language. Plus, a campus ambassador for Good Molecules will be speaking and handing out FREE product packs! Food will be provided😊 Don’t miss out on this exciting event!

messages.name: Maggie Tiernan
messages.text: Get ready for BDAA Feud this Tuesday, March 25 at 7:30 PM in Pomerene 260! It's a unique take on Family Feud that lets everyone join in the fun. Food will be provided, so bring your friends and come have some fun!

messages.name: Maggie Tiernan
messages.text: Reminder that we have a meeting tonight with Harman Thind from Microsoft!!! See you all there😁

messages.name: Maggie Tiernan
messages.text: Join us on Tuesday, March 18 at 7:30 PM in Pomerene 260 for an exciting meeting with Harman Thind, a Project Manager at Microsoft!  He'll be joining us via Zoom to share what a day in his life looks like and give us an inside look at Microsoft. 🙌🏼 Food will be provided! Have questions? Stick around for a Q&A session afterward. See you there!
